BBNaija’s ex-housemate Tuoyo has survived an auto-crash in Lagos. The reality TV show star shared a video of his badly damaged vehicle after the accident, which occurred on Ozumba Mbadiwe Road, Victoria Island, Lagos. “I just had a terrible accident but I am grateful to God that I survived as well as all those in the vehicle. I can’t believe this but thank God,” he said.   Toyin Abraham invites Timi Dakolo to lit up husband’s…     Lagos announces plans to immortalise Sound Sultan     Uzodinma appoints Cubana Chief Priest Special Adviser   He shared a post on his Instagram page with the caption: “Thank God for life and everyone that was with me. Nothing shall take our life this year in Jesus name.” - Advertisement - Tuoyo, a model and actor, became popular after he participated in the BBNaija lockdown edition, which was won by Laycon.